headline: Q3 Rundown: Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE:SWK) Vs Other Professional Tools and Equipment Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how professional tools and equipment stocks fared in Q3, starting with Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE:SWK).
